summary: The document is an identification form within the JFK ASSASSINATION SYSTEM, detailing information about David Reed Fromer, including personal details and file numbers. It was initially classified as CONFIDENTIAL but was later regraded to UNCLASSIFIED on 2 September 1994. The form references an exhibit cover sheet and a letter dated 1 February 1967 from the Bureau of Investigation in Milwaukee, Wisconsin.
key_findings: Document is part of the JFK ASSASSINATION SYSTEM identification records.
Concerns David Reed Fromer, with personal details and file numbers provided.
Originally classified as CONFIDENTIAL, later regraded to UNCLASSIFIED.
References an exhibit and a letter from the Bureau of Investigation, Milwaukee.
